AssetIndex - Class in com.ezrebclan.asset.core
An AssetIndex is a JSON-Serializable object that holds information about an Asset, including the name and type of data.
It also holds a JSONObject, AssetIndex.details, which can contain anything you want it to.
AssetIndex(String, String, JSONObject) - Constructor for class com.ezrebclan.asset.core.AssetIndex
Use this constructor to set the asset's name, storedname, and details all in one fell swoop.
AssetIndex(String, String) - Constructor for class com.ezrebclan.asset.core.AssetIndex
This constructor sets the asset's name and storedname, and it also sets the asset's details to a EmptyDetails object.
AssetIndex(JSONObject) - Constructor for class com.ezrebclan.asset.core.AssetIndex
